{"tid":2503255,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"玩緊Gamejam想問下大家意見","createTime":"2021-04-25T02:41:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T02:09:16.000Z","uid":268272,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cfcf35a794bb33438a1658ed6146913e97018dd6","tid":2503255,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T02:41:13.000Z","msg":"大家好，<a href=\"http://ldjam.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fldjam.com&d=41Q62glp5DA2hxteu4KnmcjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=6d82acf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ldjam.com</a>出了一個關於地底的game jam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暫時有一個構想，是建基於Burrow這個動畫的<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=apx1aUP3MqA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dapx1aUP3MqA&d=41Q62glp5DA2hxteu4KnmcjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=c9ca57cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=apx1aUP3MqA</a><br />\n初步是想做一個地底的動物酒店<br />\n一開始玩家在地底中你會有一個大堂及幾個房間<br />\n會有不同的動物會到達你的酒店<br />\n你需要安排房間的次序<br />\n避免動物等候太久<br />\n住客會在房間平均住一分鐘<br />\n一分鐘時間後，動物就會走去大堂埋單<br />\n你需要去大堂點動物，才能埋單<br />\n埋單後動物就會離開<br />\n然後你就可以用嗰啲收入升級房間或者掘得更深入加多啲房<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZMG1USyaxUVca77WBT2MfJkTrV6bikj4WhNeoG31cPzp?filename=GPX1zgB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGPX1zgB.jpg&h=19025a1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暫時嘅玩法係咁<br />\n希望大家巴打鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e9bcc5c15aba43b85b9f9a5a9ad8dd38879071","tid":2503255,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T02:53:47.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b26f70f9e776fa671aafc82d1331c96ec1023b","tid":2503255,"uid":20820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T03:05:57.000Z","msg":"留名待試